OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777903631
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after 'bomb hoax'
OL,4,Chalts Peter Kay performance
OL,6,FPolice said "no items of a suspicious
OL,7,Fnature were found" after comedian
OL,8,FPeter Kay was ushered off stage mid-
OL,9,Fperformance and the audience at the
OL,10,FUtilita Arena in Birmingham was
OL,11,Fevacuated on Friday night.
OL,13,FA 19-year-old man, who was arrested on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of a bomb hoax offence,
OL,15,Fremains in custody, West Midlands
OL,16,FPolice said.
OL,18,FThe comedian's show was halted after a
OL,19,F"potential suspicious bag" was found.
OL,26,@nD@MOUoD@RO]{D@AOU{D@ZO]
