PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777903631
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after 'bomb hoax'
OL,4,Chalts Peter Kay performance
OL,6,FIn an update on Saturday morning,
OL,7,Fpolice said: "Following searches of
OL,8,Fthe Utilita Arena last night, no items
OL,9,Fof a suspicious nature were found.
OL,11,F"A 19-year-old man was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of a bomb hoax offence and
OL,13,Fremains in custody this morning as our
OL,14,Finquiries continue.
OL,16,F"We're grateful to everyone for their
OL,17,Fco-operation and understanding. As
OL,18,Falways our priority is the safety of
OL,19,Fthe public."
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777903631
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after 'bomb hoax'
OL,4,Chalts Peter Kay performance
OL,6,FWitnesses said two members of staff
OL,7,Fcame onto the stage about 45 minutes
OL,8,Finto the performance, whispered into
OL,9,FKay's ear, and then escorted him off.
OL,11,FSteve Aspinall, who was at the gig
OL,12,Fwith his wife, told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation: "Two guys came on, one
OL,14,Fwith a mic and headphones, one guy
OL,15,Fwhispered to Peter Kay and then he and
OL,16,FPeter Kay shot off down the side."
OL,18,FHe said the audience was told to look
OL,19,Ffor security guards and listen out for
OL,20,Fany announcements.
OL,26,@uD@NOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777903631
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after 'bomb hoax'
OL,4,Chalts Peter Kay performance
OL,6,F"To be honest, I thought it was part
OL,7,Fof the show at first," Mr Aspinall,
OL,8,Fwho lives in Bideford, Devon, said.
OL,10,F"It was a strange atmosphere, eerie,
OL,11,Fjust confused really (about) what was
OL,12,Fhappening.
OL,14,F"But it was alright and everyone was
OL,15,Fcalm and left quite quickly with no
OL,16,Fpanic."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@VO]rD@AOUvD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
