PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1777903631
OL,3,CTeenager in custody after 'bomb hoax'
OL,4,Chalts Peter Kay performance
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the National
OL,7,FExhibition Centre (NEC) said: "Utilita
OL,8,FArena Birmingham has been evacuated as
OL,9,Fa precaution on the advice of West
OL,10,FMidlands Police after a potential
OL,11,Fsuspicious bag was found nearby.
OL,13,F"The safety and security of our
OL,14,Fcustomers and colleagues is our
OL,15,Fhighest priority. We can confirm
OL,16,Feveryone was safely evacuated and that
OL,17,Fthe venue is secure.
OL,19,F"Ticket holders will be contacted
OL,20,Fdirectly in due course."
OL,26,@oD@_OUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@XO]
